genresAdvancedInfo.name: tamaulipas indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A relatively new music genre that emerged in the Mexican state of Tamaulipas, Tamaulipas Indie is a fusion of indie rock and traditional Mexican music. The genre is characterized by its use of acoustic guitars, trumpets, and other traditional instruments, combined with modern production techniques.
